{"tid":832642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴爆山齊士差啲過曼城","createTime":"2018-09-23T02:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T02:56:02.000Z","uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"556fc32f789c0f5c62fca37cf8a880994d07b3fb","tid":832642,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"阿歷斯山齊士轉投曼聯，紅魔領隊摩連奴大爆其實這名智利球星差點已跟曼城達成協議過檔。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴大爆阿歷斯山齊士已有隻半腳踏入曼城。曼城季初有傳已準備好6,000萬鎊，但到冬季轉會窗就轉投曼聯。對於成功收購阿歷斯山齊士，摩連奴表示其實山齊士真的差少少就加盟曼城，並將今次功勞歸於球會高層。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴續約曼聯<br />\n<br />\n摩帥表示要多得當初阿仙奴未能找到替補，所以季初不放人，加上冬季轉會窗重開時又未能達成協議，再者曼聯以米希達利恩作籌碼，曼聯才能擊敗曼城得到山齊士。"},{"pid":"524e3f0c1f8f7f517ca43d33fb51ef56837b88f3","tid":832642,"uid":124020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"全能到 pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫獌連攞到一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f20d6994d358d023dee2ef11aecef9f7419623","tid":832642,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"全能轉會高手"},{"pid":"35a06befdd32244edf681b6df2408c864097abf3","tid":832642,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"#deserveBigClub"},{"pid":"78551e407bc0824ddd0abc77ac34099979087c3c","tid":832642,"uid":119778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"摩佬暗諷哥迪奧拿：簽唔到人就為自己搵台階<br />\n<br />\n哥帥酸能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fa40104a25f86c572c14a0eeef098804c55060","tid":832642,"uid":127347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"乜人轉會去到曼聯都變廢，你睇下對面隻馬列斯轉去鏝幾撚勁"},{"pid":"74834c79431ce98967415f1b0738237c656ab6db","tid":83